cards.buttonText: Join The Live Event At 7pm ET

sections: Our live event for paid subscribers starts momentarily.
Click here to join the live Zoom webinar

that starts at 7pm ET, where U.S. Rep. Ro Khanna will be taking questions about the debt ceiling deal and the House vote that is set to take place tonight. This is an incredible opportunity, so don't miss the live event!
For those that are not able to join, we will be sharing a recording of the event later.
